        <p class="">Welcome to the internet home of Saugus Union School District (SUSD). Together, the 15 elementary schools that comprise our district provide a safe, empowering learning environment for over 10,000 prekindergarten through sixth-grade students in the Santa Clarita Valley in Northern Los Angeles County, California.</p>
