        <h2 class="">A Message from Our Superintendent</h2>
        <p class="">Welcome to the Saugus Union School District. We aim to provide the best educational setting for your family’s children and are proud to be able to cultivate their talents and abilities while preparing them for the future experiences they will encounter in adulthood. SUSD excels in teaching subjects and shaping character through involved and caring teachers who know the potential of your bright children.</p>
